# Data Directory

Download the PlantVillage dataset from Kaggle:

**URL**: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/mohitsingh1804/plantvillage

## Setup

```bash
pip install kaggle
kaggle datasets download -d mohitsingh1804/plantvillage -p ./data
unzip ./data/plantvillage.zip -d ./data/
```

## Expected Structure

```
data/
└── PlantVillage/
    ├── Apple___Apple_scab/
    ├── Apple___Black_rot/
    ├── Apple___Cedar_apple_rust/
    ├── Apple___healthy/
    ├── Blueberry___healthy/
    ...  (38 class folders total)
    └── Tomato___healthy/
```

Each folder contains leaf images in JPG format.
The dataset contains approximately 54,306 images across 38 disease/healthy classes for 14 crop species.